Ombudsman Sees German Army Facing ‘Grave Shortages,’ FTD Reports

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-08-31T06:41:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/ombudsman-sees-german-army-facing-grave-shortages-ftd-reports.html
The German military is facing
“grave shortages” of equipment for troops including practice-
and live ammunition as a result of government cuts, the
 Financial Times Deutschland  reported, citing the army ombudsman.  The military has too few large-caliber weapons to be able
to carry out its mission in  Afghanistan , the newspaper said,
citing from an unpublished report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
